         Upright, narrow columns of stems — not a fountain,
         not arching. Distinctly vertical. The blue-green
         summer culms with flat alternate leaves, and the
         fall character: copper-russet stems with fluffy
         white-silver seed tufts along the nodes.
         Multiple stems at slightly different heights,
         grouped in a tight clump. -->
