    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="badge">Ohio Native Plant</div>
      <h1>Little<em>Bluestem</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-latin">Schizachyrium scoparium</p>
      <p class="hero-tagline">A native prairie grass that stands upright through drought, turns copper-russet in autumn, and holds its form — and its colour — through the longest winters.</p>
      <div class="season-badge">✦ Blue-Green Summer · Copper Fall · Silver Winter</div>
    </div>
